[/asy] The final Answer is \sqrt{6}
 ### Proof
 First, we label the diagram: [asy] import olympiad; draw((0,0)--(sqrt(3),0)--(0,sqrt(3))--cycle); draw((0,0)--(-3,0)--(0,sqrt(3))--cycle); label("$2\sqrt{3}$",(-3/2,sqrt(3)/2),NW); label("$x$",(sqrt(3)/2,sqrt(3)/2),NE);
